Problems and Solutions 

1:  For Sanctum Token Integration:-
    1.1:  Using Sanctum: Always use Hash password to store in table for generate Sanctum Token
    1.2:  Some setting needs to do when we use Sanctum Token i.e; Http->kernal.php we must add this 
    'api' => [
        \Laravel\Sanctum\Http\Middleware\EnsureFrontendRequestsAreStateful::class,
        \Illuminate\Routing\Middleware\ThrottleRequests::class.':api',
        \Illuminate\Routing\Middleware\SubstituteBindings::class,
    ],
2: csrf token issue when using swagger: in middleware folder -> verifycsrftoken file we have to add 
this code ->  "/api/*" inside the except array. added swagger code in controller


